# .trivyignore — suppression list for Trivy scans.
#
# Format (one per line):
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN        # suppress a specific CVE (filesystem + image scans)
#   AVD-XXX-NNNN          # suppress a Trivy IaC (Aqua Vuln DB) rule id
#   # <justification>     # always precede the id with a justification comment
#
# Policy:
#   - Entries MUST be reviewed every 90 days.
#   - Entries MUST link to an advisory / upstream tracker.
#   - If the finding is exploitable, fix it — do not suppress.
#   - PRs that add entries require review by a CODEOWNER of /SECURITY.md.
#
# (intentionally empty — add entries below this line)
